------------------------------- ------- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[allegro-5.0.11.zip]               4.0M Source code for all platforms in
                                        DOS/Windows friendly format.

[allegro-5.0.11.tar.gz]            3.2M Source code for all platforms in Unix
                                        friendly format.

[allegro-5.0.11.7z]                2.4M Source code for all platforms in DOS/Windows
                                        friendly format.

